    <JadeMethod name="initTblPilotLaunch" id="b30199af-121f-4607-adef-c677e4ef9a78">
        <updating/>
        <source>initTblPilotLaunch() updating;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
15 May 2019	jlgsl4	TFS 44438 - PEL1 - Multiple Pilot Launches for one movement

